      <span class="line"><span class="cmd">cd </span>~/dev/my-project</span>
      <span class="line"><span class="cmd">cell </span><span class="arg">claude</span></span>
    </div>
    <p class="stacks-more">First run scaffolds config and builds the <strong>ultimate</strong> stack (~5 min). You get the full toolchain, all MCP servers, GUI desktop, and stealth Chromium out of the box.</p>
  </section>
